Speak in sleeping
A few children speak during the night.
I do not refer to those who woke up very awake by about something that happened the day before, but the children who speak during their sleep.
The first time this has happened that may surprise you, but in reality it does not matter.
It is a benign lack of sleep called somniloquie.
It is quite often, especially among children and adolescents.
It is sure that there are more than one who speaks during the night.
This phenomenon can be very sporadic (once in life, for example, associated with an episode of strong foot), or a more regular (every day, once a week, once a month...), the day after the child does not remember anything.
There is no single, which determines its appearance
They are often linked to other changes of sleep as the nightmares, the night terrors which were, the énurésies pipi to bed at night (be) or sleepwalking, but it is not always the case.
As we have said before, they can also be associated with very high fever, to situations of stress or become agitated.
In any case it is a phenomenon little studied.
The intensity with which it happens is also very different.
It may be that he speaks with a small, quiet voice, with words alone, murmurs or with cries of tears, long speeches...
In cases where the somniloquie is very common, it would be good to see the child and consult a specialist, to see if there is a problem which causes a lot of anxiety and in order to obtain an explanation for this problem.
We have said that this is a distortion benign, that is why there is no treatment, unless it is linked to a distortion of sleep that can be treated (for example, if it is linked to a apnée of sleep or of stress).
What we can do is take into account a number of very simple precautions such as:
Try not to arouse the child before to go to sleep.
Therefore seek games calm and avoid the programmes or television series that are more or less violent.
With children very nervous and who have difficulty relax, relaxation techniques can be used to help calm internally.
This will allow children to have a more peaceful sleep.
As soon as the somniloquies are trying to stay calm.
Remind you that they are harmless for the child and that the next day it will remember most of what happened.
Useful advice
Do not wake up.
It is unnecessary since it is unconscious and you réveilleriez.
Even if he speaks, he is sleeping and is therefore.
Remind you that if it is very anxious several times, it is advisable to consult a doctor or check what causes both of anxiety in children.
If you understand what he says (which is not usual), have not the temptation to the question to obtain information.
You will achieve nothing, because in sleeping, it is not aware to hold his thinking.
More, you will hear what he said, but you will not know what it is dreaming, suddenly made attention to the way in which you interpréterez information and the conclusions you draw from this.
Are ever to the child that you can ask for the night to know his secret.
Not inform.
This causes a lot of anxiety.
In conclusion, don't worry, it is nothing of bad, it is an episode that has lasted only a few minutes.
